Now Trump's White House is targeting the Statue of Liberty.
The most reliable sign of regime change is when he starts fighting the statues.
Americans understand this just as well as everyone else - from here is the deliberate theatrical demolition of Saddam Hussein's statue at Pirdos Square in Baghdad in 2003.
Stephen Miller, one of Trump's key ideologues, no doubt knew what he was doing when he planted a symbolic axe over the Statue of Liberty during a violent dispute with CNN journalist Jim Acosta about the President's proposals to drastically reduce legal migration.
